    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207090/extras/7c589c5540709ff2b668948f083e45fd.poster.avif?t=1771635779\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207090/extras/7c589c5540709ff2b668948f083e45fd.webm?t=1771635779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207090/extras/7c589c5540709ff2b668948f083e45fd.mp4?t=1771635779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是 Rogue-lite 机甲动作射击游戏<strong>《钢铁巨像》</strong>的试玩版。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该试玩版包含一个独立任务，搭配经典刺激的随机强化升级系统，在这个变化多端的未来世界中，为新老玩家提供极具策略性的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207090/extras/57d7bfa11b0db183626bce21e31cefec.poster.avif?t=1771635779\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207090/extras/57d7bfa11b0db183626bce21e31cefec.webm?t=1771635779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207090/extras/57d7bfa11b0db183626bce21e31cefec.mp4?t=1771635779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任务设定在过去，当时人类正在与远古武器<strong>“盖亚”</strong>交战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须控制一台名为<strong>“基加斯”</strong>的机甲，与四面八方袭来的敌人作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207090/extras/baa68c73f0925aad92b278a12ede10ec.poster.avif?t=1771635779\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207090/extras/baa68c73f0925aad92b278a12ede10ec.webm?t=1771635779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207090/extras/baa68c73f0925aad92b278a12ede10ec.mp4?t=1771635779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巧妙运用红外对抗系统（IRCM）抵御源源不断的子弹和导弹攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在运输船抵达前，使用一切必要的手段生存下来。</p>",
